LABEL: 0x52

ENG: I mean, it'd be weird if I could.

JPN: 例によって、ぶらぶらしている。

ENG: Probably best not to think about it...

LABEL: 0x576
ENG: "Can you take care of it again?"

LABEL: 0x694
ENG: Shiroha set about cooking the fish.

LABEL: 0x6b2
JPN: 俺はそれを待っている。

LABEL: 0x9c6
JPN: 「一緒に材料を用意して、料理をして食べて」

LABEL: 0xa0a
JPN: 「けっこう盛りだくさんなイベントこなしたのに、会話が１つもなかったよね」
ENG: "We did a bunch of stuff, really, but we barely said a word to each other!"

LABEL: 0xab0
ENG: "I don't think there's really anything wrong with that."

LABEL: 0xade
JPN: 「いや、根本的に間違ってる気がする」
ENG: "No, it's definitely wrong on a fundamental level."

LABEL: 0xb2c
ENG: "Mmh. I don't really get it, but..."

LABEL: 0xbcc
JPN: 改まって言われると、照れくさいが。
ENG: Hearing it put in those terms made it kind of embarrassing.

LABEL: 0xd16
JPN: 改まって振られると、何をしゃべったらいいのか。
ENG: I have a second chance at conversation, but what should I say?

LABEL: 0xe6e
ENG: "You could make some good money off this stuff."

JPN: 俺の褒め言葉に、しろははあまりうれしそうじゃない。

ENG: "I don't make it because I want to make money."

ENG: "And there's no way I'd measure up to a professional, either."

LABEL: 0xff8
JPN: 「まぁ、ちゃんと勉強してる人は違うんだろうね」
ENG: "I mean, people who really put the work into studying cooking are probably on a whole different level."

JPN: 「そういえば、うちの近くに、調理の専門学校があったな」
ENG: "Speaking of which, isn't there a culinary school near here?"

JPN: 「友達が学校辞めて、通ってた」
ENG: "A friend of mine dropped out to enroll there."

LABEL: 0x11f2
JPN: なんとなく、ちょっとだけじゃないような気がした。

LABEL: 0x1232

JPN: 「卒業したら、そういう進路もありだよな」

ENG: Impossible? What is, attending a culinary school?

ENG: "Umm... By a lot of reasons, could you possibly mean..."

LABEL: 0x16de
ENG: "Something about how you're a special person."

JPN: 「そういうのなんか、かっこいいよな」

JPN: 「ごめん。そんな気軽なものじゃないか」
ENG: "Sorry. I guess I shouldn't be so casual about it, huh?"

LABEL: 0x17ca
JPN: 「……あまり関わっちゃだめとか聞いた？」
ENG: "...Did you also hear about how you shouldn't get too involved with me?"

LABEL: 0x1832

ENG: "I mean, they might've said something along those lines."

LABEL: 0x1b0e

LABEL: 0x1c04
ENG: "It happens when I hate things, I think."

LABEL: 0x1c46
ENG: "Because I don't want them to get close to me."

LABEL: 0x1f04
ENG: "And then, you'll be engulfed in flames..."

LABEL: 0x2000

LABEL: 0x2296

ENG: "Please, hurry up and get off of this island!"

JPN: 「いや、そんなこと急に言われても……」
ENG: "No, I mean, it's way too sudden for me to..."

LABEL: 0x419e

LABEL: 0x4206

ENG: "I'll make sure you get a proper burial."

JPN: おそるおそる、口の中へ。

ENG: But it was spicy on a surprisingly normal level.
